Package com.xekri.leakvm.sdk.net.server

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    AsyncDataResponseCallback
    AsyncDataResponseCallback interface must be implemented by any callback whose instances are intended to handle an asynchronic callback to write on the HTTP Stream.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AsyncDataResponse
    AsyncDataResponse class is the implementation of HTTP Response, handle asynchronic responses.
    AsyncServerRequest
    AsyncServerRequest class handles an Asynchronic HTTP Request
    DataBoundary
    DataBoundary class is the implementation for handle files on an HTTP Request
    DataContent
    DataContent class is the implementation for Data Content (JSON/XML)
    DataRequest
    DataRequest class is the implementation of HTTP Request, this contains Client Headers, GET, POST and Boundary Data.
    DataResponse
    DataResponse class is the implementation of HTTP Response, handle customizable responses.
    ServerRequest
    The ServerRequest class must be implemented by any callback whose instances are intended to handle a http request over a thread.
    SyncDataResponse
    SyncDataResponse class is the implementation of HTTP Response, handle synchronic responses.
    SyncServerRequest
    SyncServerRequest class handles an Synchronic HTTP Request
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    ResponseStatus
    ResponseStatus Enumeration handles the HTTP response codes and messages
